ſomtime of holy matrimonie, yea
ſomtime of the ioyes of heauen, &amp; paines of
hell, making fooliſh &amp; vaine playes of theſe
thinges. The vſe or ende of all the worke
of the Lorde towardes him, to preach and
ſet forth the power and glory of the eternall
kingdome of God. Pſal. 145. 11. 12. To vs,
that wee and our poſteritie may better

know, truſt, loue, and feare the Lorde, Pſal.
78. 7. Deut. 4. 9. But contrariwiſe, we neuer
